            "style": "",
            "text": "Just from a performance perspective, the 2021 Ram 1500 TRX will smoke some of the best sports cars and muscle cars out there with a stated quarter-mile time of just 12.9 seconds and a 0-60 mph time of 4.5 seconds, but as you can tell, this truck isn't a modern version of the ",
